ked decentralized development. Particular attention is paid to the philosophical comprehension of the value and semantic foundations laid down in the National Project ""Culture"", where the improvement and modernization of the processes of socio- cultural activities are to ensure systemic, multifaceted, large-scale, replicable, social effectiveness of local projects. Communicative principles of interdepartmental and inter-sectoral interaction, cooperation with institutions of civil society significantly changes the quality of cultural environment and the artistic life of society in the Russian regions, coordinating it with the level of national and world culture. IJASOS- International E-Journal of Advances in Social Sciences, Vol. IV, Issue 12, December 2018 http://ijasos.ocerintjournals.org 561",2018,,rclone_drive,tattochka1977 tattochka1977,project management; sociocultural sphere; dialogue thinking; communicative paradigm,of the entire,en,cultural; development; culture; socio; management; policy; project; russian; social; human; sustainable; capital
